#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/core.md:1
msgid "Core Lua API"
msgstr "Core Lua API"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/core.md:3
msgid ""
"`ptool` exposes these core runtime helpers directly under `ptool` and `p`."
msgstr "`ptool` 会直接在 `ptool` 和 `p` 下暴露这些核心运行时辅助能力。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/core.md:5
msgid ""
"`ptool run <lua_file>` runs a Lua script and injects the global variable "
"`ptool` (or its alias `p`; for example, `p.run` is equivalent to `ptool.run`)"
". For files ending in `.lua`, `ptool <lua_file>` is a CLI shortcut with the "
"same behavior."
msgstr ""
"`ptool run <lua_file>` 会运行 Lua 脚本，并注入全局变量 `ptool` （以及它的别名"
" `p`；例如 `p.run` 与 `ptool.run` 等价）。对于以 `.lua` 结尾的文件，`ptool "
"<lua_file>` 也是一个行为相同的 CLI 快捷写法。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/core.md:10
msgid ""
"The embedded Lua runtime keeps the base Lua globals and exposes only these "
"standard libraries by default:"
msgstr "内嵌的 Lua 运行时会保留基础 Lua 全局能力，并默认只暴露这些标准库："

