msgid "`v0.1.0` - Introduced."
msgstr "`v0.1.0` - 引入。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/core.md:50
msgid "`ptool.use` declares the minimum required `ptool` version for a script."
msgstr "`ptool.use` 用来声明脚本所要求的最低 `ptool` 版本。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/core.md:56
msgid ""
"The argument is a semantic version string (SemVer) and supports an optional "
"`v` prefix, such as `v0.1.0` or `0.1.0`."
msgstr "参数是一个语义化版本字符串（SemVer），可选带 `v` 前缀，例如 `v0.1.0` 或 "
"`0.1.0`。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/core.md:58
msgid ""
"If the required version is higher than the current `ptool` version, the "
"script exits immediately with an error saying that the current `ptool` "
"version is too old."
msgstr "如果要求的版本高于当前 `ptool` 版本，脚本会立即退出，并报错说明当前 `ptool` "
"版本过旧。"

