msgstr "ptool.ask.confirm"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/core.md:175
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/core.md:175"
msgid "`v0.5.0` - Introduced."
msgstr "`v0.5.0` - 引入。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/core.md:177
msgid ""
"`ptool.ask.confirm(prompt[, options])` asks the user for a yes/no answer."
msgstr "`ptool.ask.confirm(prompt[, options])` 向用户询问一个是/否答案。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/core.md:179
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/core.md:179"
msgid "`prompt` (string, required): The prompt shown to the user."
msgstr "`prompt`（string，必填）：展示给用户的提示语。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/core.md:180
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/core.md:180"
msgid "`options` (table, optional): Prompt options. Supported fields:"
msgstr "`options`（table，可选）：提示选项。支持："

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/core.md:180
msgid ""
"`default` (boolean, optional): Default answer used when the user presses "
"Enter without typing."
msgstr "`default`（boolean，可选）：用户直接按 Enter 时采用的默认答案。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/core.md:180
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/core.md:180"
msgid "`help` (string, optional): Extra help text shown below the prompt."
msgstr "`help`（string，可选）：显示在提示下方的额外帮助文本。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/core.md:184
