msgstr "返回值会在 runtime 启动时固定下来，之后不会随着 `ptool.cd(...)` 改变。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/core.md:360
msgid "In `ptool repl`, this returns `nil`."
msgstr "在 `ptool repl` 中，它会返回 `nil`。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/core.md:362
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/core.md:362"
msgid "Example:"
msgstr "示例："

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/core.md:370
msgid "ptool.try"
msgstr "ptool.try"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/core.md:372
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/core.md:372"
msgid "`v0.4.0` - Introduced."
msgstr "`v0.4.0` - 引入。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/core.md:374
msgid ""
"`ptool.try(fn)` runs `fn` and converts raised errors into return values."
msgstr "`ptool.try(fn)` 会执行 `fn`，并把抛出的错误转换成返回值。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/core.md:376
msgid "`fn` (function, required): Callback to execute."
msgstr "`fn`（function，必填）：要执行的回调。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/core.md:377
msgid "Returns: `ok, value, err`."
msgstr "返回：`ok, value, err`。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/core.md:379
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/core.md:379"
msgid "Return value rules:"
msgstr "返回值规则："

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/core.md:381
msgid ""
"On success, `ok = true`, `err = nil`, and `value` contains the callback "
"result."
msgstr "成功时，`ok = true`，`err = nil`，`value` 是回调返回结果。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/core.md:383
msgid "If the callback returns no values, `value` is `nil`."
msgstr "如果回调没有返回值，`value` 为 `nil`。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/core.md:384
msgid "If the callback returns one value, `value` is that value."
msgstr "如果回调只返回一个值，`value` 就是该值本身。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/core.md:385
msgid ""
"If the callback returns multiple values, `value` is an array-like table."
msgstr "如果回调返回多个值，`value` 是一个类数组 table。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/core.md:386
msgid "On failure, `ok = false`, `value = nil`, and `err` is a table."
msgstr "失败时，`ok = false`，`value = nil`，`err` 是一个 table。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/core.md:388
msgid "Structured error fields:"
msgstr "结构化错误字段："

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/core.md:390
msgid ""
"`kind` (string): Stable error category such as `io_error`, `command_failed`, "
"`invalid_argument`, `http_error`, or `lua_error`."
msgstr ""
"`kind`（string）：稳定的错误类别，例如 `io_error`、`command_failed`、 "
"`invalid_argument`、`http_error` 或 `lua_error`。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/core.md:392
msgid "`message` (string): Human-readable error message."
msgstr "`message`（string）：便于阅读的错误消息。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/core.md:393
msgid "`op` (string, optional): API or operation name such as `ptool.fs.read`."
msgstr "`op`（string，可选）：发生错误的 API 或操作名，例如 `ptool.fs.read`。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/core.md:394
msgid "`detail` (string, optional): Extra detail for the failure."
msgstr "`detail`（string，可选）：额外的失败细节。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/core.md:395
msgid "`path` (string, optional): Path involved in a filesystem failure."
msgstr "`path`（string，可选）：文件系统错误涉及的路径。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/core.md:396
msgid ""
"`input` (string, optional): Original input that failed to parse or validate."
msgstr "`input`（string，可选）：解析或校验失败时的原始输入。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/core.md:397
msgid "`cmd` (string, optional): Command name for command failures."
msgstr "`cmd`（string，可选）：命令执行失败时的命令名。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/core.md:398
msgid ""
"`status` (integer, optional): Exit status or HTTP status when available."
msgstr "`status`（integer，可选）：退出码或 HTTP 状态码（如果可用）。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/core.md:399
msgid "`stderr` (string, optional): Captured stderr for command failures."
msgstr "`stderr`（string，可选）：命令失败时捕获到的 stderr。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/core.md:400
msgid "`url` (string, optional): URL involved in an HTTP failure."
msgstr "`url`（string，可选）：HTTP 失败涉及的 URL。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/core.md:401
msgid ""
"`cwd` (string, optional): Effective working directory for command failures."
msgstr "`cwd`（string，可选）：命令执行时实际使用的工作目录。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/core.md:402
msgid ""
"`target` (string, optional): SSH target for SSH-related command failures."
msgstr "`target`（string，可选）：SSH 相关命令失败时的目标主机。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/core.md:403
msgid ""
"`retryable` (boolean): Whether retrying may make sense. Defaults to `false`."
msgstr "`retryable`（boolean）：是否适合重试。默认值为 `false`。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/core.md:405
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/core.md:405"
msgid "Behavior:"
msgstr "行为说明："

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/core.md:407
msgid ""
"`ptool` APIs raise structured errors. `ptool.try` converts them into the "
"`err` table above so callers can branch on `err.kind` and related fields."
msgstr ""
"`ptool` 自带 API 抛出的都是结构化错误。`ptool.try` 会把它们转换成上面的 `err`"
" table，方便调用方根据 `err.kind` 和其他字段做分支处理。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/core.md:409
msgid ""
"Plain Lua errors are also caught. In that case, `err.kind` is `lua_error`, "
"and only `message` is guaranteed."
msgstr "普通 Lua 错误也会被捕获。这种情况下，`err.kind` 为 `lua_error`，并且只保证 "
"`message` 一定存在。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/core.md:411
msgid ""
"`ptool.try` is the recommended way to handle errors from APIs such as "
"`ptool.fs.read`, `ptool.http.request`, `ptool.run(..., { check = true })`, "
"and `res:assert_ok()`."
msgstr ""
"对于 `ptool.fs.read`、`ptool.http.request`、`ptool.run(..., { check = true })"
"` 和 `res:assert_ok()` 这类 API，推荐使用 `ptool.try` 来做错误处理。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/core.md:415
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/core.md:415"
msgid "Example:"
msgstr "示例："

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/core.md:440
msgid "ptool.run"
msgstr "ptool.run"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/core.md:442
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/core.md:442"
msgid "`v0.1.0` - Introduced."
msgstr "`v0.1.0` - 引入。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/core.md:444
msgid "`ptool.run` executes external commands from Rust."
msgstr "`ptool.run` 从 Rust 执行外部命令。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/core.md:446
msgid "The following call forms are supported:"
msgstr "支持以下调用形式："

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/core.md:458
msgid "Argument rules:"
msgstr "参数规则："

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/core.md:460
msgid ""
"`ptool.run(cmdline)`: `cmdline` is split using shell-style (`shlex`) rules. "
"The first item is treated as the command and the rest as arguments."
msgstr ""
"`ptool.run(cmdline)`：`cmdline` 会按 shell 风格（`shlex`）规则拆分。第一项 作"
"为命令，其余项作为参数。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/core.md:462
msgid ""
"`ptool.run(cmd, argsline)`: `cmd` is used directly as the command, and "
"`argsline` is split into an argument list using shell-style (`shlex`) rules."
msgstr ""
"`ptool.run(cmd, argsline)`：`cmd` 直接作为命令，`argsline` 会按 shell 风格 （"
"`shlex`）规则拆分成参数列表。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/core.md:464
msgid ""
"`ptool.run(cmd, args)`: `cmd` is a string and `args` is an array of strings."
msgstr "`ptool.run(cmd, args)`：`cmd` 是字符串，`args` 是字符串数组。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/core.md:465
msgid ""
"`ptool.run(cmdline, options)`: `options` overrides settings for this "
"invocation, such as `echo`."
msgstr "`ptool.run(cmdline, options)`：`options` 会覆盖本次调用的配置，例如 `echo`。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/core.md:467
msgid ""
"`ptool.run(cmd, args, options)`: `args` can be either a string or an array "
"of strings, and `options` overrides settings for this invocation, such as "
"`echo`."
msgstr ""
"`ptool.run(cmd, args, options)`：`args` 可以是字符串，也可以是字符串数组； "
"`options` 会覆盖本次调用的配置，例如 `echo`。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/core.md:469
msgid "`ptool.run(options)`: `options` is a table."
msgstr "`ptool.run(options)`：`options` 是一个 table。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/core.md:470
msgid ""
"When the second argument is a table: if it is an array "
"(consecutive integer keys `1..n`), it is treated as `args`; otherwise it is "
"treated as `options`."
msgstr "当第二个参数是 table 时：如果它是数组（连续整数键 `1..n`），则视为 `args`； "
"否则视为 `options`。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/core.md:473
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/core.md:473"
msgid "Return value rules:"
msgstr "返回值规则："

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/core.md:475
msgid "A table is always returned with the following fields:"
msgstr "总是返回一个 table，包含以下字段："

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/core.md:475
msgid "`ok` (boolean): Whether the exit code is `0`."
msgstr "`ok`（boolean）：退出码是否为 `0`。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/core.md:475
msgid ""
"`code` (integer|nil): The process exit code. If the process was terminated "
"by a signal, this is `nil`."
msgstr "`code`（integer|nil）：进程退出码。如果进程因信号终止，则为 `nil`。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/core.md:475
msgid "`cmd` (string): Command name used for the execution."
msgstr "`cmd`（string）：本次执行使用的命令名。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/core.md:475
msgid "`cwd` (string): Effective working directory used for the execution."
msgstr "`cwd`（string）：本次执行实际使用的工作目录。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/core.md:475
msgid "`stdout` (string, optional): Present when `stdout = \"capture\"`."
msgstr "`stdout`（string，可选）：当 `stdout = \"capture\"` 时提供。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/core.md:475
msgid "`stderr` (string, optional): Present when `stderr = \"capture\"`."
msgstr "`stderr`（string，可选）：当 `stderr = \"capture\"` 时提供。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/core.md:475
msgid ""
"`assert_ok(self)` (function): Raises a structured error when `ok = false`. "
"The error kind is `command_failed`, and the error may include `cmd`, `status`"
", `stderr`, and `cwd`."
msgstr ""
"`assert_ok(self)`（function）：当 `ok = false` 时抛出结构化错误。错误类别 为 "
"`command_failed`，并且可能包含 `cmd`、`status`、`stderr` 和 `cwd`。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/core.md:486
msgid ""
"The default value of `check` comes from `ptool.config"
"({ run = { check = ... } })`. If not configured, it defaults to `false`. "
"When `check = false`, callers can inspect `ok` themselves or call "
"`res:assert_ok()`."
msgstr ""
"`check` 的默认值来自 `ptool.config({ run = { check = ... } })`。如果未配置， "
"默认是 `false`。当 `check = false` 时，调用方可以自行检查 `ok`，或者调用 "
"`res:assert_ok()`。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/core.md:489
msgid ""
"When both `check = true` and `retry = true`, `ptool.run` asks whether the "
"failed command should be retried before raising the final error."
msgstr ""
"当同时设置 `check = true` 和 `retry = true` 时，`ptool.run` 会在最终抛错前， "
"询问是否要重试失败的命令。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/core.md:491
msgid ""
"When `check = true`, `ptool.run` raises the same structured `command_failed` "
"error that `res:assert_ok()` raises. Use `ptool.try(...)` if you want to "
"catch and inspect it from Lua."
msgstr ""
"当 `check = true` 时，`ptool.run` 抛出的也是与 `res:assert_ok()` 相同的 "
"`command_failed` 结构化错误。如果你想在 Lua 里捕获并检查它，使用 `ptool.try"
"(...)`。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/core.md:495
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/core.md:495"
msgid "Example:"
msgstr "示例："

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/core.md:516
msgid ""
"`ptool.run(options)` is also supported, where `options` is a table with the "
"following fields:"
msgstr "也支持 `ptool.run(options)` 形式，其中 `options` 是一个包含以下字段的 table："

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/core.md:519
msgid "`cmd` (string, required): The command name or executable path."
msgstr "`cmd`（string，必填）：命令名或可执行文件路径。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/core.md:520
msgid "`args` (string[], optional): The argument list."
msgstr "`args`（string[]，可选）：参数列表。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/core.md:521
msgid "`cwd` (string, optional): The child process working directory."
msgstr "`cwd`（string，可选）：子进程工作目录。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/core.md:522
msgid ""
"`env` (table, optional): Additional environment variables, where keys are "
"variable names and values are variable values."
msgstr "`env`（table，可选）：附加环境变量，键和值都应为字符串。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/core.md:524
msgid ""
"`echo` (boolean, optional): Whether to echo command information for this "
"execution. If omitted, the value from `ptool.config({ run = { echo = ... } })"
"` is used; if that is also unset, the default is `true`."
msgstr ""
"`echo`（boolean，可选）：本次执行是否回显命令信息。如果省略，则使用 "
"`ptool.config({ run = { echo = ... } })` 中的值；若仍未设置，则默认是 `true`"
"。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/core.md:527
msgid ""
"`check` (boolean, optional): Whether to raise an error immediately when the "
"exit code is not `0`. If omitted, the value from `ptool.config"
"({ run = { check = ... } })` is used; if that is also unset, the default is "
"`false`."
msgstr ""
"`check`（boolean，可选）：退出码不为 `0` 时是否立即抛错。如果省略，则使用 "
"`ptool.config({ run = { check = ... } })` 中的值；若仍未设置，则默认是 "
"`false`。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/core.md:530
msgid ""
"`confirm` (boolean, optional): Whether to ask the user for confirmation "
"before execution. If omitted, the value from `ptool.config"
"({ run = { confirm = ... } })` is used; if that is also unset, the default "
"is `false`."
msgstr ""
"`confirm`（boolean，可选）：执行前是否询问用户确认。如果省略，则使用 "
"`ptool.config({ run = { confirm = ... } })` 中的值；若仍未设置，则默认是 "
"`false`。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/core.md:533
msgid ""
"`retry` (boolean, optional): Whether to ask the user whether to retry after "
"a failed execution when `check = true`. If omitted, the value from "
"`ptool.config({ run = { retry = ... } })` is used; if that is also unset, "
"the default is `false`."
msgstr ""
"`retry`（boolean，可选）：当 `check = true` 时，执行失败后是否询问用户是否重"
"试。 如果省略，则使用 `ptool.config({ run = { retry = ... } })` 中的值；若仍"
"未设置， 则默认是 `false`。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/core.md:537
msgid ""
"`stdout` (string, optional): Stdout handling strategy. Supported values:"
msgstr "`stdout`（string，可选）：stdout 处理策略。支持："

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.6.0/lua-api/core.md:537
